      "detail": "Post-training/RL processing means exhaust is used for reinforcement learning from human feedback and preference optimization. This processing mode directly converts user interaction data into model capability improvement. RLHF is the specific technical mechanism through which exhaust arbitrage creates competitive advantage. Post-training processing is where the unclaimed byproduct becomes the economic centre of the deal."
    },
    "Derivation": {
